{"tid":1922280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透：西班牙政府考慮馬德里封城　阻病毒國內傳播","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T13:04:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad294f42c2adce61f9eff389c4410b195cc2ed8","tid":1922280,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"武漢新型冠狀病毒疫情在歐洲多國蔓延，其中西班牙逾 2000 人確診，當中 47 人死亡。根據《路透社》報道，西班牙馬德里自治區主席阿尤索今日表示，西班牙政府正考慮將馬德里封城（was considering locking down Madrid），以防病毒在該國傳播。但西班牙政府昨日否認有關做法。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，阿尤索在西班牙第五電視台表示，根據過去的觀察，正考慮關閉馬德里的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F-%E8%A5%BF%E7%8F%AD%E7%89%99%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E9%A6%AC%E5%BE%B7%E9%87%8C%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E-%E9%98%BB%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%2589%2599%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2592%25AD%2F&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e77c4b7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%2589%2599%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2592%25AD%2F&h=fcfc9b29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/so